meta.name: Turf Wars
meta.description: Team territory-control. Capture zones, earn tick points over time, first to target wins or highest score at time cap.

derived.controlPercent: time-weighted zone control share per team

capture.effect: set controller(zoneId)=team; start/continue scoring on tick

decapture.effect: set controller(zoneId)=null; no scoring from zone

matchStart: Engines hot  Turf Wars begins! Three zones live.
